OL,3,CMurder jury hears man who admits
OL,4,Cfiring gun did not know weapon was
OL,5,Cloaded
OL,7,FA man who has admitted being the
OL,8,Fgunman who fired into the house of a
OL,9,Fgrandfather in County Durham has told
OL,10,Fa murder trial that he had not
OL,11,Frealised the weapon was loaded with
OL,12,Flive ammunition.
OL,14,FBarry Dawson, 60, died from a single
OL,15,Fgunshot to his heart in a downstairs
OL,16,Froom of his home on Elm Street, in
OL,17,FStanley, in April this year.
