OL,3,CMurder jury hears man who admits
OL,4,Cfiring gun did not know weapon was
OL,5,Cloaded
OL,7,FSean Reay, 30, of Clavering Place, in
OL,8,Fthe town, denies his murder, but has
OL,9,Fpreviously admitted in court that it
OL,10,Fis him captured on CCTV firing the
OL,11,Fhandgun directly into the house.
OL,13,FHe is jointly charged with four other
OL,14,Fmen with murdering Mr Dawson. They all
OL,15,Fdeny the charge.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
