OL,3,CMurder jury hears man who admits
OL,4,Cfiring gun did not know weapon was
OL,5,Cloaded
OL,7,FReay told jurors at Teesside Crown
OL,8,FCourt on Wednesday (15 October) that
OL,9,Fhe did not know the firearm had live
OL,10,Fbullets in it because he had never
OL,11,Fshot a gun before, adding that he had
OL,12,Fnot checked the weapon.
OL,14,FGiving evidence in his own defence,
OL,15,FReay said he had been involved in a
OL,16,Fheated argument outside his own home
OL,17,Fearlier in the day involving a man
OL,18,Finside a vehicle whose name he refused
OL,19,Fto confirm.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
