OL,3,CMurder jury hears man who admits
OL,4,Cfiring gun did not know weapon was
OL,5,Cloaded
OL,7,FReay denied claims that his real
OL,8,Ftarget had never been Mr Dawson - but
OL,9,Feither his son or another man inside
OL,10,Fthe house and the 60-year-old had "got
OL,11,Fin the way".
OL,13,FThe CCTV footage also shows Reay's co-
OL,14,Fdefendant, Kelvin Lawson, smashing the
OL,15,Fwindow before the gun is fired.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
