OL,3,CMurder jury hears man who admits
OL,4,Cfiring gun did not know weapon was
OL,5,Cloaded
OL,7,FHe told the jury that it must have
OL,8,Fbeen because he had found some bullets
OL,9,Fin an old coal bunker in the garden
OL,10,Fthat he rented in 2020 which he had
OL,11,Fhandled before selling in exchange for
OL,12,Fdrugs three years later.
OL,14,FReay and Lawson both deny murder.
OL,16,FKevin Dorward, 38, of New Durham Road,
OL,17,FStanley, Thomas Sterling, 23, of The
OL,18,FAvenue, Stanley, and Keith Dorward,
OL,19,F48, of no fixed abode all deny murder
OL,20,Fand the trial continues.
